description: #00030 Mr. Messy in pen 220111 was created 11th January 2022, this was Iris' drawing of her favourite "Mr. Man" (Books by Roger Hargreaves), Mr. Messy. This is NFT number 30 released by the Youngest Artist in the NFT World, Iris. Age at release - 3 years old.
